================================================================================

DATA ATTRIBUTION

The Sanskrit declension data contained in this application was manually 
extracted and compiled from the following sources:

    • Sabda Manjari (Primary reference book)
    • My Coaching - Sanskrit grammar resources
    • Learn Sanskrit - Educational materials
    • Sanskrit Abhyas - Practice resources

This data compilation represents original work and significant effort in 
digitizing traditional Sanskrit grammar resources.

